response.overview: Stardom Mid Summer Champions 2023 was a professional wrestling event promoted by World Wonder Ring Stardom. The event took place on July 2, 2023, in Yokohama, Japan, at the Yokohama Budokan.  • Waka Tsukiyama & Yuna Mizumori vs. Queen's Quest (Hina & Miyu Amasaki)  • Six Man Tag Team Match  Aya Sakura & STARS (Hazuki & Saya Iida) vs. HANAKO, Mei Seira & Suzu Suzuki • Queen's Quest (AZM, Lady C, Saya Kamitani & Utami Hayashishita) vs. STARS (Hanan, Koguma, Mayu Iwatani & Momo Kohgo)  • Oedo Tai (Momo Watanabe, Natsuko Tora, Rina & Ruaka) vs. Donna del Mondo (Giulia, Maika, Mai Sakurai & Thekla) • Nanae Takahashi vs. Starlight Kid • Goddesses Of Stardom Title Match Club Venus (Mariah May & Mina Shirakawa) (c) vs. God's Eye (Ami Sourei & Syuri) • High Speed Title Match  Saki Kashima (c) vs. Fukigen Death • Wonder Of Stardom Title Match  Tam Nakano (c) vs. MIRAI  • Indian Strap Match Natsupoi vs. Saori Anou.
response.title: Stardom Mid Summer Champions 2023
